OL,3,CCoventry's U-turn on budget cuts but
OL,4,Ccouncil tax still set to rise
OL,6,FCoventry City Council has released its
OL,7,Fnew budget plans in an attempt to save
OL,8,Fmore money for next year.
OL,10,FSome proposed plans were scrapped,
OL,11,Fhowever taxpayers will be spending
OL,12,Fmore, it has been confirmed.
OL,14,FWhat was the outcome of the meeting?
OL,16,FMany budget cuts to public services
OL,17,Fthat were found unpopular with the
OL,18,Fpublic are now not going ahead.
